{"tid":1530694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［國際戰線］大家唔好忽略左默克爾訪華！","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:27:35.000Z","uid":284061,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2d7b76c6d655964c925f807b985be054b291f6ac","tid":1530694,"uid":284061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"默克爾9月5日至7日訪華！！！<br />\n擬與中方領導人談香港局勢<br />\n要知道上次默克爾見完中共領導人，放左劉霞<br />\n<br />\n請用所有方法推所有有關警暴同集會遊行自由既問題 <br />\n推到默克爾/德國駐港領事館關注！！<br />\n<br />\n德國駐港領事館Facebook:<br />\nGerman Consulate General Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾將於下周四至周六（9月5日至7日）率領商業代表團訪問中國，並與中方領導人會面。柏林墨卡托中國研究中心副總裁胡謐空（Mikko Huotari）預料，默克爾訪華時會談及香港局勢，一旦香港警民衝突在周末惡化，默克爾訪華行程可能會調整。<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190831/mobile/bkn-20190831092051552-0831_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190831%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190831092051552-0831_00822_001.html&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=d694f4cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190831/mobile/bkn-20190831092051552-0831_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ebbdaffdd26cefa45dc3e93fbdbed2255f248eea","tid":1530694,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"Chinazi"},{"pid":"b98e2392c234aa0d967906f6cf0c46caef228421","tid":1530694,"uid":2582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾左膠<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"937eecc42539c02d886c16f2fcddd127e9b605a6","tid":1530694,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"德國應該繼續左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6e83df46e9fdd2661fbfb0c283e4ff4174d811","tid":1530694,"uid":76538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"冇學生用成個暑假去幫我地抗爭, 我地點撚樣捱到今日??<br />\n<br />\n就係今日, 佢地著番校服, 被迫服從呢個洗腦